### Room API Test

### 환경 변수 설정
# @no-cookie-jar
# @name variables

### 1. 호스트 테스트 사용자 생성
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/test/create-test-user?nickname=호스트
Content-Type: application/json

> {%
    client.global.set("HOST_USER_ID", response.body.data.userId);
    client.global.set("HOST_JWT", response.body.data.accessToken);
    client.log("호스트 UserId: " + response.body.data.userId);
    client.log("호스트 JWT: " + response.body.data.accessToken);
%}

###

### 2. 로그인 사용자 생성
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/test/create-test-user?nickname=로그인유저
Content-Type: application/json

> {%
    client.global.set("USER_JWT", response.body.data.accessToken);
    client.log("로그인유저 JWT: " + response.body.data.accessToken);
%}

###

### 3. 방 생성 (POST /rooms) - 호스트
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rooms
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{HOST_JWT}}

{
  "roomName": "함께하는 쇼핑",
  "targetBudget": 500000,
  "syncMode": "FOLLOW",
  "roomMeta": {
    "shoppingPurpose": "친구들과 함께하는 겨울 쇼핑",
    "interestCategories": ["패션", "전자제품", "가구"],
    "headcount": 4,
    "budgetMin": 100000
  }
}

> {%
    client.global.set("ROOM_ID", response.body.data.roomId);
    client.global.set("ROOM_CODE", response.body.data.roomCode);
    client.log("Room ID: " + response.body.data.roomId);
    client.log("Room Code: " + response.body.data.roomCode);
%}

###


### 4. 방 조회 - ID로 조회 (GET /rooms/{roomId})
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/1

###

### 5. 방 조회 - 초대 코드로 조회 (GET /rooms/code/{roomCode})
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/code/ED4C89B7

###

### 6. 로그인 사용자 방 입장 (POST /rooms/join)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/join
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{USER_JWT}}

{
  "roomCode": "ED4C89B7"
}

###

### 7. 게스트 방 입장 (POST /rooms/join/guest)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/join/guest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomCode": "ED4C89B7",
  "nickname": "게스트1"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("GUEST_JWT", response.body.data.accessToken);
    client.log("게스트 JWT: " + response.body.data.accessToken);
%}

###

### 8. 참여자 목록 조회 (GET /rooms/{roomId}/members)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/1/members

###

### 9. 방 나가기 (DELETE /rooms/{roomId}/leave) - 로그인 사용자
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/1/leave
Authorization: Bearer {{USER_JWT}}

###

### 10. 동기화 모드 변경 (PATCH /rooms/{roomId}/sync-mode) - 호스트만 가능
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/1/sync-mode
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{HOST_JWT}}

{
  "syncMode": "FREE"
}

###

### 11. 호스트 URL 업데이트 (PATCH /rooms/{roomId}/host-url) - FOLLOW 모드, 호스트만 가능
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/1/host-url
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{HOST_JWT}}

{
  "currentUrl": "https://example.com/product/123"
}

###

### 12. 내 상태 업데이트 (PATCH /rooms/{roomId}/my-state) - 호스트
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/1/my-state
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{HOST_JWT}}

{
  "isCameraOn": true
}

###

### 13. 내 상태 업데이트 (PATCH /rooms/{roomId}/my-state) - 게스트
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/1/my-state
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{GUEST_JWT}}

{
  "isCameraOn": false
}

###

### 14. 방 종료 (POST /rooms/{roomId}/close) - 호스트만 가능
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/1/close
Authorization: Bearer {{HOST_JWT}}
###